reviews.review_text: toward the end for keith you can hear someone, I think Jerry, saying "quiet" right when keith starts to bang away right after "i know that the life im livins no good." this is right before he was replaced by brent
Smokin' Supplication! I must say, there are hotter supplications, but Jer's wailing riffs towards the end are very noteworthy and energetic. Overall, not the best, but man... fun!
